  "S02madadh_u:89": "anuttaro lokānukampakaḥ /",
  "S02madadh_u:90": "mama sarvasattvānāṃ ca rakṣāṃ kurvantu /",
  "S02madadh_u:91": "paritrāṇaṃ parigrahaṃ paripālanaṃ śāntiṃ svastyayanaṃ daṇḍaparihāraṃ śastraparihāraṃ viṣadūṣaṇaṃ viṣanāśanaṃ sīmābandhaṃ dharaṇībandhaṃ ca kurvantu /",
